videos.description: Julius Randle brings the ball down the court, puts the ball on a string and dribbles around his defenders before passing it to Immanuel Quickley for a 3-pointer.

videos.description: Mitchell Robinson gets up for the block before Immanuel Quickley runs the break, dropping it off to RJ Barrett who scores inside for the Knicks.

videos.description: RJ Barrett gets a pass off of the inbounds then wraps a pass around his defender to Mitchell Robinson on the other side to throws it down.
